slot.description: Name of web app slot. If not specified then will default to production slot.

details.description: If true, metric details are included in response

filter.description: Return only usages/metrics specified in the filter. Filter conforms to odata syntax. Example: $filter=(name.value eq 'Metric1' or name.value eq 'Metric2') and startTime eq '2014-01-01T00:00:00Z' and endTime eq '2014-12-31T23:59:59Z' and timeGrain eq duration'[Hour|Minute|Day]'.

nextlink.description: Link to next page of resources
